data.description: **Open House 11/19/23 12PM to 3PM**This Salem home, centrally located, boasts 3 BDR, 2 BA, and a LFT, ensuring spacious living. The combined living spaces are complemented by a modern kitchen with a gas stove and sleek appliances. The main floor features a large MBR with an ensuite. Enjoy efficient ductless heating. Both the roof and water heater has a 9-year warranty, updated siding. Has an RV space, a 24x24 garage, and a garden shed. Sale is contingent on the seller securing a replacement home.
